  <section id="about">
    <h2>About This Project</h2>
    <p>This datastore explores the current state of global climate action through data-driven visualizations and diagnostics. It was created to support UN Sustainable Development Goal 13: Climate Action.</p>
    <p>We use public datasets and analytics tools to highlight key patterns in emissions, climate impacts, and policy response. Our goal is to raise awareness and promote smarter climate decisions based on evidence.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="visuals">
    <h2>Visualizations</h2>
